# ğŸ“Œ Bash Script Create

```bash
nano vari.sh
```

```bash
#!/bin/bash
echo "Hey, what's your name?"
read name
echo "Welcome, $name"
```

### Run Script

```bash
chmod +x vari.sh
./vari.sh
```

